restrictions on
birth control coverage in the
new political

00:22.956 --> 00:24.258 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
climate.

00:24.291 --> 00:27.160 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Plus: part two of
