00:48.482 --> 00:57.791 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: The Islamic State
group has
claimed responsibility tonight
for the Berlin

00:57.824 --> 01:01.995 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
truck attack that killed a dozen
people and
injured 50.

01:02.029 --> 01:07.134 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
That word came hours after
German police let
their main suspect go.

01:07.167 --> 01:10.203 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Special correspondent Malcolm
Brabant reports
from Berlin.

01:10.237 --> 01:16.243 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MALCOLM BRABANT: This normally
bustling Christmas
market was eerily quiet today,
as investigators

01:16.276 --> 01:18.111 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
searched for clues.

01:18.145 --> 01:22.616 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Swathed in fog, and with armed
guards sealing
off the area, Berlin was coming
to terms with

01:22.649 --> 01:28.288 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
its new status as a victim of
terrorism, after
Paris, Brussels and Nice.

01:28.322 --> 01:30.891 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
German Chancellor Angela Merkel
spoke at a
morning news conference.

01:30.924 --> 01:33.894 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ANGELA MERKEL, German Chancellor
(through
translator): There is still a
lot that we

01:33.927 --> 01:39.132 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
don't know about this act with
sufficient
certainty, but we must, as
things stand, assume

01:39.166 --> 01:40.934 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
it was a terrorist attack.

01:40.968 --> 01:45.472 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MALCOLM BRABANT: Police detained
a Pakistani
asylum-seeker shortly after the
truck rammed

01:45.505 --> 01:47.240 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
into a crowd of people on
Monday.

01:47.274 --> 01:52.112 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But, today, he was released, due
to insufficient
evidence.

01:52.145 --> 01:55.215 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Prosecutors said he matched a
description
of the suspected attacker, but
he denied any

01:55.248 --> 01:56.984 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
involvement.

01:57.017 --> 02:02.522 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The truck, which had been
carrying steel beams,
was towed away earlier this
morning.

02:02.556 --> 02:06.093 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The body of a Polish truck
driver was found
inside the cabin.

02:06.126 --> 02:09.129 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
He had been stabbed and shot
after being hijacked.

02:09.162 --> 02:10.964 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
The gun used to kill him has yet
to be found.

02:10.998 --> 02:11.999 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
PETER NEUMANN, Director,
International Center
for the Study of Radicalization,
King's College:

02:12.032 --> 02:13.934 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
It was waiting to happen, no?

02:13.967 --> 02:15.969 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
I'm not, like, totally
surprised.

02:16.003 --> 02:19.606 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MALCOLM BRABANT: Berlin is the
hometown of
terrorism expert Peter Neumann.

02:19.639 --> 02:24.945 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
He believes German authorities
were too complacent
about the possibility of an
attack and didn't

02:24.978 --> 02:27.647 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
offer sufficient protection to
the Christmas
markets.

02:27.681 --> 02:32.652 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
PETER NEUMANN: I think, in
Germany, people
have been very blessed with the
idea that

02:32.686 --> 02:35.355 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
they would be spared this kind
of attack.

02:35.389 --> 02:39.526 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And so I don't think that German
authorities
were thinking as systematically
about the

02:39.559 --> 02:44.431 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
threat from terrorism as
authorities in Britain
have or authorities in other
countries.

02:44.464 --> 02:46.233 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
This will have to change.

02:46.266 --> 02:51.204 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
And there will be a very
uncomfortable discussion
in Germany about anti-terrorism
measures,

02:51.238 --> 02:56.610 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
but also, of course, about the
relationship
with Muslim communities and with
refugees.

02:56.643 --> 03:01.314 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MALCOLM BRABANT: The chancellor
and other
senior officials laid white
roses at a makeshift

03:01.348 --> 03:03.350 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
memorial to the victims.

03:03.383 --> 03:07.220 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
They toured the market and were
briefed by
senior police officers.

03:07.254 --> 03:12.526 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Ordinary Berliners paid their
respects, laying
candles, flowers and messages of
sympathy.

03:12.559 --> 03:17.164 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Many said they believe this
attack marked
a turning point for Germany,
especially as,

03:17.197 --> 03:21.568 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
for most of the past 24 hours,
they were under
the impression that the massacre
had been

03:21.601 --> 03:27.674 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
perpetrated by an asylum-seeker
admitted under
Chancellor Merkel's open-door
refugee policy.

03:27.707 --> 03:33.547 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WOMAN: I definitely want to see
stricter border
control in Germany and in the
European Union.

03:33.580 --> 03:39.820 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I think I want to see more
cooperation between
the countries of the European
Union and regarding

03:39.853 --> 03:42.656 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
refugee policy, because, at the
moment, it's
out of control.

03:42.689 --> 03:50.330 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MAN: I think it's not yet today
the time to
think about the consequences for
the refugee

03:50.363 --> 03:52.199 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
politics.

03:52.232 --> 04:01.942 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I think today it's a question of
sadness and
come here, see people come
together, and bring

04:01.975 --> 04:02.943 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
flowers.

04:02.976 --> 04:04.077 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
And that's most important.

04:04.111 --> 04:08.415 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And I think we have a good
system of asylum-seekers.

04:08.448 --> 04:12.652 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MALCOLM BRABANT: Chancellor
Merkel warned
against letting the attack
change Germans'

04:12.686 --> 04:16.890 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
way of life, but she
acknowledged her policies
were under new pressure.

04:16.923 --> 04:21.228 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
ANGELA MERKEL (through
translator): I know
that it would be particularly
hard for us

04:21.261 --> 04:25.832 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
all to bear it if it were to be
confirmed
that a person committed this
crime who sought

04:25.866 --> 04:28.468 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
protection and asylum in
Germany.

04:28.502 --> 04:33.006 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
This would be particularly
sickening for the
many, many Germans who work to
help refugees

04:33.039 --> 04:37.744 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
every day and for the many
people who really
need our help and are making an
effort to

04:37.777 --> 04:39.646 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
integrate in our country.

04:39.679 --> 04:43.783 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MALCOLM BRABANT: At the Berlin
State Parliament,
where flags were lowered to
half-mast, the

04:43.817 --> 04:49.322 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
anti-immigrant Alternative for
Germany Party
and its regional deputy leader,
Ronald Glaser,

04:49.356 --> 04:51.158 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
offered a harsher appraisal.

04:51.191 --> 04:52.792 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
RONALD GLASER, Alternative for
Germany Party:
First of all, the terrorist is
to blame for

04:52.826 --> 04:54.628 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
what happened.

04:54.661 --> 05:01.067 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
On the other hand, Angela Merkel
and her welcome
culture made all these refugees
come to our

05:01.101 --> 05:02.235 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
country.

05:02.269 --> 05:04.538 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And among them were a lot of
fanatics and
criminals.

05:04.571 --> 05:10.243 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
She's not going to accept that
her policy
was wrong, but, of course, the
German people

05:10.277 --> 05:14.514 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
is awakening and they maybe will
force her
to do so.

05:14.548 --> 05:18.385 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MALCOLM BRABANT: Just outside
the regional
parliament is the largest
remaining section

05:18.418 --> 05:23.223 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
of the Berlin Wall, whose demise
27 years
ago led to Europe's open
borders.

05:23.256 --> 05:28.228 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
There could not be a more
poignant reminder
of what's at stake as Europe
grapples with

05:28.261 --> 05:31.498 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
terrorism and the wave of
migration across
the Mediterranean.

05:31.531 --> 05:35.035 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
In the meantime, the German
capital remains
on high alert.

05:35.068 --> 05:37.837 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
KLAUS KANDT, Berlin Police Chief
(through
translator): Of course people
are worried.

05:37.871 --> 05:40.340 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I believe people who live in the
city should
be vigilant.

05:40.373 --> 05:44.778 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MALCOLM BRABANT: Security has
also been tightened
at Christmas markets and other
outdoor venues

05:44.811 --> 05:48.615 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
all across Europe, out of an
abundance of
caution.

05:48.648 --> 05:52.986 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And in Berlin this evening,
mourners gathered
for a candlelight vigil in the
same square

05:53.019 --> 05:58.391 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
where the tragedy took place, as
Germany's
leaders attended a solemn
memorial service

05:58.425 --> 06:00.260 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
at a nearby church.

06:00.293 --> 06:05.665 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The iconic Brandenburg Gate was
illuminated
with the images of both the
German and Berlin

06:05.699 --> 06:06.800 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
flags.

06:06.833 --> 06:10.237 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And Malcolm joins
me now from
Berlin.

06:10.270 --> 06:16.576 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Malcolm, now that ISIS has
claimed responsibility,
how is that affecting thinking
there?

06:16.610 --> 06:22.015 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MALCOLM BRABANT: It's not really
made that
much of an impact, to be honest.

06:22.048 --> 06:27.120 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The German interior minister
acknowledged
that ISIS had made this claim,
but he didn't

06:27.153 --> 06:28.455 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
really react to it.

06:28.488 --> 06:30.590 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
I don't think anybody is
particularly surprised.

06:30.624 --> 06:34.394 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
This attack was right out of the
jihadist
playbook.

06:34.427 --> 06:37.998 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It's the sort of language in the
claim that
they have made that they have
used before.

06:38.031 --> 06:45.505 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But what, I think, ISIS has
achieved by saying
what they have done is that they
have perhaps

06:45.538 --> 06:47.440 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
helped to polarize Germany.

06:47.474 --> 06:54.648 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
They have helped to perhaps
drive people into
the arms of the Alternative for
Germany Party,

06:54.681 --> 06:56.716 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
the right-wing anti-immigrant
party.

06:56.750 --> 06:58.652 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And they're going to create
hatred.

06:58.685 --> 07:01.288 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And that's really what their
main objective
is.

07:01.321 --> 07:05.892 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: So, the
perpetrator is still
on the loose.

07:05.925 --> 07:09.763 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Is there fear that he or she may
strike again?

07:09.796 --> 07:13.233 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
MALCOLM BRABANT: That certainly
is the worry.

07:13.266 --> 07:16.102 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And people are being advised to
stay indoors.

07:16.136 --> 07:18.638 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
The police are very much
concerned.

07:18.672 --> 07:22.742 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The interior minister did say
that they do
have some leads and that the
police are following

07:22.776 --> 07:24.577 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
