Christmas market,
and was in touch with police all
the time.

07:43.897 --> 07:48.535 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But it now appears that he may
have actually
lost sight of the target during
that particular

07:48.568 --> 07:51.905 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
time, which is perhaps why the
wrong man was
arrested.

07:51.938 --> 07:55.975 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But there are certainly fears
that there will
be attacks again, and there are
armed police

07:56.009 --> 07:58.611 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
