around there.

07:58.645 --> 08:04.784 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
One pretty good indication of
just how tense
things are, there was a federal
prosecutor

08:04.818 --> 08:08.788 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
