markets, which
is hardly an endorsement of the
state of security

08:13.660 --> 08:14.627 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
here.

08:14.661 --> 08:15.628 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: No, it isn't.

08:15.662 --> 08:17.464 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Malcolm Brabant in Berlin, thank
you.

08:17.497 --> 08:21.568 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: In the day's
other news:
Turkish police detained seven
people in the

08:21.601 --> 08:24.037 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
