still waiting
for transport.

09:20.560 --> 09:26.266 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Meanwhile, in Moscow, Russia,
Iran and Turkey
announced they're ready to
broker a final

09:26.299 --> 09:30.770 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Syrian peace, leaving President
