29:02.774 --> 29:03.842 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
DR.

29:03.875 --> 29:05.711 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
STACEY LEIGH RUBIN: It is a real
surge in
interest.

29:05.744 --> 29:10.215 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
LISA DESJARDINS: An IUD is
usually plastic
and inserted in the uterus to
prevent pregnancy.

29:10.248 --> 29:15.253 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
IUDs are considered among the
most effective
birth control methods, but
they're not cheap,

29:15.287 --> 29:16.254 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
running up to $1,000.

29:16.288 --> 29:18.023 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
DR.

29:18.056 --> 29:20.225 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
STACEY LEIGH RUBIN: So, what
questions do
you have about these different
methods and

29:20.258 --> 29:21.994 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
what do you think you're leaning
towards?

29:22.027 --> 29:27.532 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
LISA DESJARDINS: Right now, for
Victoria and
other women, IUDs and all birth
control is

29:27.566 --> 29:32.938 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
free, because the Obama
administration considers
it a preventative procedure, a
category that

29:32.971 --> 29:37.876 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
