most important

29:43.849 --> 29:46.618 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
reasons we must win on November
8.

29:46.652 --> 29:50.722 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
LISA DESJARDINS: President-elect
Donald Trump
campaigned on repealing and
replacing the

29:50.756 --> 29:52.290 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Affordable Care Act.

29:52.324 --> 29:57.229 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
