talked about
it.

30:00.532 --> 30:03.635 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
MIKE PENCE (R), Vice
President-Elect: I'm
a Christian, a conservative and
a Republican,

30:03.669 --> 30:04.636 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
in that order.

30:04.670 --> 30:06.438 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
(CHEERING AND APPLAUSE)

30:06.471 --> 30:09.574 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
LISA DESJARDINS: vice
president-elect Mike
Pence, speaking on a radio show
in October,

30:09.608 --> 30:14.279 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
highlighted religious groups
opposed to contraception,
and their religious freedom.

30:14.312 --> 30:17.182 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MIKE PENCE: Our administration
is going to
err on the side of freedom.

30:17.215 --> 30:21.319 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
We are going to err on the side
of protecting
the liberties of our people.

30:21.353 --> 30:25.290 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
LISA DESJARDINS: A key voice
will be Mr. Trump's
pick to head the Department of
Health and

30:25.323 --> 30:29.928 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Human Services, orthopedic
