30:36.902 --> 30:38.303 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
REP.

30:38.336 --> 30:39.438 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
TOM PRICE (R), Georgia: Bring me
one woman
who has been left behind.

30:39.471 --> 30:40.639 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Bring me one.

30:40.672 --> 30:42.441 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
There's not one.

30:42.474 --> 30:46.211 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The fact of the matter is, this
is a trampling
on religious freedom and
religious liberty

30:46.244 --> 30:47.746 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
in this country.

30:47.779 --> 30:51.683 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
LISA DESJARDINS: Price's old
comment struck
an already watchful Internet.

30:51.717 --> 30:56.988 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Immediately after the election,
Google searches
for IUD spiked and Twitter saw
phrases like

30:57.022 --> 31:00.325 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
