31:00.358 --> 31:02.160 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
What are the wallet
implications?

31:02.194 --> 31:08.133 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
A University of Pennsylvania
study found that
the Obama contraception policy
saved IUD and

31:08.166 --> 31:12.270 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
birth control pill users an
average of roughly
$250 a year.

31:12.304 --> 31:13.939 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
DR.

31:13.972 --> 31:16.274 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
STACEY LEIGH RUBIN: No-cost
birth control
has been a game-changer for
women.

31:16.308 --> 31:22.848 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And the idea of going back to
high out-of-pocket
costs for contraception is
distressing.

31:22.881 --> 31:26.885 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
LISA DESJARDINS: But will Trump
change those
costs?

31:26.918 --> 31:29.688 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Someone with insight is Marjorie
Dannenfelser.

31:29.721 --> 31:34.993 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
