Pro-Life Coalition,
and runs the anti- abortion
group the Susan

31:35.026 --> 31:36.862 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
B. Anthony List.

31:36.895 --> 31:41.933 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
