nor Trump want
to weigh in on the morality of
contraception,

31:41.967 --> 31:44.002 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
but when it comes to the no-cost
mandate:

31:44.035 --> 31:46.838 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
MARJORIE DANNENFELSER,
President, Susan B.
Anthony List: He and I also
agree that religious

31:46.872 --> 31:52.043 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
and any individual deserves the
right to a
conscience, and they shouldn't
be forced to

31:52.077 --> 31:54.980 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
pay for things that they find
are undermining
of that conscience.

31:55.013 --> 31:59.551 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, yes, I believe that he will
undo that
mandate, and he will be right to
do so.

31:59.584 --> 32:04.289 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
LISA DESJARDINS: That leads to
another question
about the president-elect: How
quickly could

32:04.322 --> 32:09.094 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
a President Trump change
contraception coverage,
and therefore out-of-pocket
cost?

32:09.127 --> 32:10.195 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Relatively quickly.

32:10.228 --> 32:13.098 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
You see, the contraception
mandate is not
a law.

32:13.131 --> 32:15.534 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
