32:15.567 --> 32:22.440 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And HHS, under a Trump White
House, could
change that rule without input
from Congress.

32:22.474 --> 32:26.945 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Women like Victoria are making
decisions now,
as she and her friends remain
uncertain.

32:26.978 --> 32:32.017 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
VICTORIA CROSS: We talked a lot
about our
own reproductive health and
where do we go

32:32.050 --> 32:36.721 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
from here and how do we prepare
for this new
administration, where our access
may go away?

32:36.755 --> 32:41.593 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
LISA DESJARDINS: Victoria's new
birth control
will last up to five years.

32:41.626 --> 32:46.131 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
