50:10.207 --> 50:11.275 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
BRUCE SPRINGSTEEN: Yes, that's
true.

50:11.308 --> 50:13.077 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: So, did you lose
touch with
them?

50:13.110 --> 50:14.845 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Did they lose touch with you?

50:14.879 --> 50:20.517 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
BRUCE SPRINGSTEEN: It was just a
very divided
