was.

50:38.969 --> 50:45.142 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: In this book, you
often talk
about telling your story, but
also telling

50:45.175 --> 50:49.413 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
