through in your
music, right, telling a story of
this country.

50:49.446 --> 50:50.414 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
BRUCE SPRINGSTEEN: Yes.

50:50.447 --> 50:51.649 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
Yes.

50:51.682 --> 50:53.617 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: How do we bridge
divides in
this country?

50:53.651 --> 50:59.356 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
BRUCE SPRINGSTEEN: I think you
