generalize about them.

51:03.294 --> 51:09.466 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I know people on both sides of
that particular
divide.

51:09.500 --> 51:12.503 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And they just have a different
opinion about
it.

51:12.536 --> 51:18.776 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, I think that maybe look
outside your own
daily experience also, which is
something

51:18.809 --> 51:25.983 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
that, as a writer, that was sort
